highlights.text: Taylor Swift has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Anti-Hero” is the highest at #1.
“Here With Me” by d4vd is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 37 spots at #134.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 301 weeks straight.
“Rich Flex” by Drake and 21 Savage is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #2.
